View

Class PhotoViewController

  • java.lang.Object
    • View.PhotoViewController

  • public class PhotoViewController
extends java.lang.Object
    PhotoViewController is the class associated with the screen for displaying an Albums main page. This page allows the user to view thumbnails of all photos that exist in the selected album. It also allows the user to add, edit and delete tags from photos, add new photos, delete photos, add/edit captions, move and copy photos, view photos from a selected thumbnail image in a larger screen, and view the photos in a slideshow
    Author:
    Tom Raybould & Mike Tomkowich
